description: Lone Star Samwiches aims to offer an open air dining experience from its mobile food unit with a variety of regional American-samwich-favorites with a multi-cultural flare. The 'samwiches' will be prepared with only the best local ingredients, served fresh, and only made to order. Each 'samwich' is a representative of the melting pot that is unique to the City of Houston.
name: Lone Star Samwiches
